1
00:00:03,520 --> 00:00:06,160
You wanted to see me?
To give me a test?

2
00:00:06,310 --> 00:00:08,520
The Crystal Empire has returned.

3
00:00:08,670 --> 00:00:11,740
You want me to help protect
an entire empire?

4
00:00:11,890 --> 00:00:14,050
It must be you, and you alone.

5
00:00:14,550 --> 00:00:16,360
But, what if I fail?

6
00:00:16,510 --> 00:00:18,040
Let's just say the empire...

7
00:00:18,190 --> 00:00:19,700
isn't the only thing that's returned.

8
00:00:21,390 --> 00:00:22,700
Go, go!

9
00:00:22,850 --> 00:00:25,710
Sparklriffic!

10
00:00:25,860 --> 00:00:28,770
With Cadance putting all her strength
into keeping her spell going,

11
00:00:28,920 --> 00:00:31,670
and me trying to keep an eye
on signs of trouble in the arctic,

12
00:00:31,820 --> 00:00:35,250
we haven't been able to gather
much information from the Crystal Ponies.

13
00:00:35,400 --> 00:00:36,670
There are Crystal Ponies?!

14
00:00:36,820 --> 00:00:38,000
I wish I could help you.

15
00:00:38,150 --> 00:00:42,010
But I can't seem to remember anything
before King Sombra came to power.

16
00:00:43,430 --> 00:00:45,680
History of the Crystal Empire.

17
00:00:45,820 --> 00:00:49,150
The last page of the book mentioned
a crystal heart as the fair's centerpiece,

18
00:00:49,300 --> 00:00:52,100
so I used my magic to cut one
out of a crystal block.

19
00:00:52,250 --> 00:00:56,140
The whole purpose of the Crystal Fair
is to lift the spirits of the Crystal Ponies,

20
00:00:56,290 --> 00:00:58,090
so the light within them
can power the Crystal Heart,

21
00:00:58,240 --> 00:00:59,740
so that the empire can be protected!

22
00:00:59,920 --> 00:01:02,110
I think we may have
a problem...

23
00:01:02,260 --> 00:01:04,200
I didn't know it was an actual relic!

24
00:01:04,350 --> 00:01:05,950
It's alright, Twilight.

25
00:01:06,580 --> 00:01:07,830
Twilie...

