00:01:58,680 --> 00:02:00,460
The empire is under attack.

30
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:23,300
I have to find the Crystal Heart!

31
00:02:23,450 --> 00:02:25,640
No, you stay here with Cadance.

32
00:02:25,780 --> 00:02:27,600
She needs you, Shining Armor.

33
00:02:28,740 --> 00:02:30,130
I'll retrieve the Heart.

34
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:31,540
Let's do this.

35
00:02:31,690 --> 00:02:34,830
I've been trying to figure out
how I'm meant to pass Celestia's test.

36
00:02:34,980 --> 00:02:37,300
Retrieving the Crystal Heart must be it.

37
00:02:37,450 --> 00:02:39,200
But there is something else you can do.

38
00:02:39,350 --> 00:02:40,150
Name it.

39
00:02:40,300 --> 00:02:42,890
You and the rest of our friends
have to keep the fair going.

40
00:02:43,040 --> 00:02:46,120
What? With that thing
moving into the empire?!

41
00:02:46,270 --> 00:02:49,750
The whole purpose of the Crystal Fair
is to lift the spirits of the Crystal Ponies,

42
00:02:49,900 --> 00:02:51,750
so they can activate the Crystal Heart.

43
00:02:51,900 --> 00:02:53,130
Yeah, and?

44
00:02:53,280 --> 00:02:57,100
If the Crystal Ponies find out King Sombra
is trying to take over the empire again,

45
00:02:57,250 --> 00:02:59,950
their spirits are gonna be
anything but lifted.

46
00:03:01,750 --> 00:03:05,470
It won't matter if I find the Crystal Heart.
They won't be able to make it work.

47
00:03:05,620 --> 00:03:08,020
You have to keep them happy
here at the fair.

48
00:03:08,170 --> 00:03:11,240
Keep the fair going and
the Crystal Ponies' spirits high.

49
00:03:11,490 --> 00:03:12,950
Done and done.

50
00:03:13,700 --> 00:03:16,250
Twilie,
be careful.

51
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:17,240
I will.

52
00:03:49,660 --> 00:03:53,960
I just found out they're offering
face painting for the little ones.

53
00:03:58,270 --> 00:04:01,030
We can do that.
Twilight's doing what?!

54
00:04:02,330 --> 00:04:07,370
He... really... loves
getting his face painted.

55
00:04:09,350 --> 00:04:11,480
Who wants a flugelhorn?

56
00:04:11,630 --> 00:04:13,380
I want a flugelhorn!

57
00:04:14,050 --> 00:04:16,370
Who else wants a flugelhorn?

58
00:04:16,520 --> 00:04:18,630
I want a flugelhorn!!

59
00:04:22,450 --> 00:04:23,730
Twilight, wait!

60
00:04:24,400 --> 00:04:25,570
I'm coming with you!

61
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:29,390
You can't. I have to retrieve
the Crystal Heart by myself.

62
00:04:30,010 --> 00:04:33,530
I know. I promise
I won't lift a claw to help you.

63
00:04:35,580 --> 00:04:37,290
Not a claw, Spike.

64
00:04:38,870 --> 00:04:40,450
Where are we going, exactly?

65
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:43,540
I think I might know where
King Sombra hid the Crystal Heart.

66
00:04:43,790 --> 00:04:45,040
The castle?

67
00:04:45,190 --> 00:04:46,460
The king would've been
counting on the fact

68
00:04:46,610 --> 00:04:49,150
that nopony would dare
come looking for it here.

69
00:04:49,310 --> 00:04:51,040
They'd've been too afraid to even try.

70
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:53,040
I hope you're right.

71
00:04:53,190 --> 00:04:54,670
You and me both.

72
00:05:04,750 --> 00:05:06,500
What are you lookin' at?!

73
00:05:06,990 --> 00:05:08,720
That's what I thought!

74
00:05:09,790 --> 00:05:11,530
Uh, Rainbow Dash?

75
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:13,850
We're supposed to be actin'
like nothing's wrong.

76
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:15,100
Exactly!

77
00:05:17,750 --> 00:05:20,590
What I mean is,
maybe you should let me

78
00:05:20,740 --> 00:05:22,880
keep the Crystal Ponies away
from the fake heart,

79
00:05:23,030 --> 00:05:25,480
while you show off
your joustin' skills.

80
00:05:25,930 --> 00:05:31,150
Seeing my awesomeness does have a way
of putting ponies into a pretty good mood.

81
00:05:38,950 --> 00:05:41,650
Come on, Knight Fluttershy.

82
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:43,430
It's showtime.

83
00:05:44,260 --> 00:05:46,650
How are y'all feelin'?
Havin' a good time?

84
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:48,960
The best I've had
in over a thousand years!

85
00:05:49,110 --> 00:05:52,590
That's good! Gotta renew
that spirit of love and unity

86
00:05:52,740 --> 00:05:55,130
if you're gonna power up
that Crystal Heart, right?

87
00:05:55,290 --> 00:05:57,950
I sure would like to see it
before the ceremony.

88
00:05:58,100 --> 00:05:59,820
It's been such a long time.

89
00:05:59,970 --> 00:06:02,600
Oh, I hear ya, but,
uh... phew!

90
00:06:02,760 --> 00:06:04,790
I'm gettin' a little toasty out here.

91
00:06:04,940 --> 00:06:08,370
Bet you'd like to cool off
with a little Crystal Empire nectar!

92
00:06:12,590 --> 00:06:15,670
Uh, you tried
the Crystal Empire fritters yet?

93
00:06:15,820 --> 00:06:18,030
Made from a traditional
Crystal Empire recipe!

94
00:06:18,180 --> 00:06:19,600
You're gonna love 'em!

95
00:06:21,080 --> 00:06:23,230
I hear there's a joustin' match
about to start!

96
00:06:23,380 --> 00:06:24,900
You don't wanna miss that!

97
00:06:26,310 --> 00:06:31,110
Come on, Twilight... these Crystal Ponies
are more curious than a cat!

98
00:06:38,580 --> 00:06:41,750
It's gotta be here somewhere.
It's just gotta be!

99
00:06:43,980 --> 00:06:46,080
Not a claw, Spike.

100
00:06:48,100 --> 00:06:49,940
Celestia's orders!

101
00:06:56,460 --> 00:06:59,570
<i>If the empire is filled
with hope and love,</i>

102
00:06:59,730 --> 00:07:02,630
<i>those things are reflected
across all of Equestria.</i>

103
00:07:02,780 --> 00:07:05,610
<i>If hatred and fear take hold...</i>

104
00:07:08,850 --> 00:07:10,290
Of course!

105
00:07:12,310 --> 00:07:14,190
- What? Did you find it?!
- No!

106
00:07:14,340 --> 00:07:17,190
Because this isn't
King Sombra's castle.

107
00:07:17,340 --> 00:07:19,320
Isn't this where he lived
when he was in power?

108
00:07:19,470 --> 00:07:22,620
It is. But it didn't look like this.

109
00:07:38,440 --> 00:07:40,250
When did you learn to do that?

110
00:07:40,400 --> 00:07:42,630
That was a little trick
Celestia taught me.

111
00:07:49,260 --> 00:07:50,580
You stay here.

112
00:07:51,400 --> 00:07:52,720
If you insist.

113
00:07:58,150 --> 00:08:00,780
Can you see what's down there yet?

114
00:08:01,080 --> 00:08:04,980
Not yet. I can't even tell
how far down this goes!

115
00:08:19,700 --> 00:08:21,750
- Spike?
- Yeah?

116
00:08:21,900 --> 00:08:23,680
Can you see outside?

117
00:08:29,090 --> 00:08:34,750
<i>Yes... crystals... </i>

118
00:08:36,060 --> 00:08:40,370
It's not good! Cadance's magic
must be fading faster than before!

119
00:08:48,140 --> 00:08:50,450
Twilight?
Are you okay?

120
00:08:50,990 --> 00:08:52,250
Yes...

121
00:09:01,790 --> 00:09:03,250
What in the...

122
00:09:03,960 --> 00:09:05,090
Stop...

123
00:09:06,250 --> 00:09:07,260
moving!

124
00:09:14,400 --> 00:09:17,440
Spike, I think it's here!

125
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:26,450
What are you doing here?

126
00:09:26,600 --> 00:09:29,020
I don't know!
I opened the door and--

127
00:09:29,170 --> 00:09:30,570
And now you must go.

128
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:33,210
Go where?

129
00:09:33,360 --> 00:09:36,780
Doesn't matter to me.
You failed the test, Twilight!

130
00:09:44,750 --> 00:09:47,270
I don't understand! The test--

131
00:09:47,420 --> 00:09:50,590
Not only will you not move on
to the next level of your studies,

132
00:09:50,740 --> 00:09:53,500
you won't continue your studies at all!

133
00:09:54,500 --> 00:09:58,360
You didn't say anything about
no longer being your student if I failed!

134
00:10:00,360 --> 00:10:01,640
Didn't I?

135
00:10:02,780 --> 00:10:05,250
But... what do I do now?!

136
00:10:09,650 --> 00:10:10,990
<i>Twilight!</i>

137
00:10:11,550 --> 00:10:12,550
<i>Twilight?</i>

138
00:10:13,550 --> 00:10:14,950
Twilight!

139
00:10:15,900 --> 00:10:17,990
Twiliiiight!

140
00:10:19,260 --> 00:10:20,640
I know you told me to stay up there,

141
00:10:20,650 --> 00:10:21,850
but you were down here
for such a long time

142
00:10:21,860 --> 00:10:23,630
and you weren't answering
and I got worried so I came down here,

143
00:10:23,640 --> 00:10:25,000
and you were just
staring at that wall...

144
00:10:25,010 --> 00:10:27,550
I was calling your name, but I couldn't
seem to get your attention, and...

145
00:10:28,380 --> 00:10:32,050
What were you looking at?
I mean... it's just a wall.

146
00:10:33,500 --> 00:10:34,590
Ponyville?!

147
00:10:35,300 --> 00:10:36,310
How did I get...

148
00:10:36,460 --> 00:10:39,200
No! I don't wanna go!

149
00:10:39,350 --> 00:10:41,700
Please, Twilight, don't leave me!

150
00:10:42,730 --> 00:10:47,370
King Sombra's dark magic.
A doorway that leads to your worst fear.

151
00:10:47,860 --> 00:10:51,250
We were home... you told me
you didn't need me any more.

152
00:10:51,400 --> 00:10:53,150
You were sending me away...

153
00:10:53,300 --> 00:10:57,150
A fear that will never come to pass.
I'm never gonna send you away.

154
00:10:57,500 --> 00:10:59,550
And I'm not gonna fail my test!

155
00:11:05,100 --> 00:11:06,650
What's in there?

156
00:11:07,550 --> 00:11:08,750
Stairs.

157
00:11:09,450 --> 00:11:11,710
Lots and lots of stairs.

158
00:11:16,550 --> 00:11:18,310
Maybe you should come
with me this time.

159
00:12:04,520 --> 00:12:06,700
Bravo, knight Rainbow Dash!

160
00:12:09,680 --> 00:12:11,950
Isn't there...
somepony else who could...

161
00:12:12,100 --> 00:12:15,320
take over the jousting demonstration
with you?

162
00:12:16,310 --> 00:12:21,450
The fate of an entire empire rests on us
showing these ponies a good time.

163
00:12:21,600 --> 00:12:25,500
But, y'know,
if that isn't important to you...

164
00:12:27,640 --> 00:12:30,500
Okay, okay,
I'll take it easy on you next time.

165
00:12:30,650 --> 00:12:32,170
But not too easy.

166
00:12:32,320 --> 00:12:34,550
I've got a reputation to maintain!

167
00:12:44,970 --> 00:12:47,470
What if this is just more of his magic?

168
00:12:47,630 --> 00:12:50,020
He makes a door that links
to your worst nightmare...

169
00:12:50,170 --> 00:12:52,650
why not a staircase
that goes on forever?

170
00:12:57,800 --> 00:12:59,200
Hold on to me.

171
00:13:26,300 --> 00:13:29,650
I am running out of weaving materials
for the traditional crafts booths!

172
00:13:29,800 --> 00:13:33,230
I've just made a hat out of
three pieces of hay and a drinking straw!

173
00:13:33,380 --> 00:13:35,450
I made it work. But still!

174
00:13:35,600 --> 00:13:38,280
We gotta do everything we can
to keep this thing goin'.

175
00:13:39,450 --> 00:13:41,280
The Princess isn't lookin' so good.

176
00:13:41,430 --> 00:13:44,500
I can imagine her magic
is gonna last much longer.

177
00:13:44,650 --> 00:13:46,370
It's gonna be fine.

178
00:13:46,520 --> 00:13:49,380
These ponies are gonna power up
that Crystal Heart when the time comes,

179
00:13:49,530 --> 00:13:51,800
and we won't be needin'
her magic anyway.

180
00:13:51,950 --> 00:13:55,850
I sure hope that time comes soon!
Even I can't keep this party going forever!

181
00:14:09,200 --> 00:14:11,360
This isn't the Crystal Heart.

182
00:14:11,960 --> 00:14:14,440
Oh, of course it isn't.

183
00:14:14,590 --> 00:14:16,520
- The real one is--
- On its way!

184
00:14:16,670 --> 00:14:21,400
I was going to say 'being polished'
to buy us some more time?

185
00:14:21,550 --> 00:14:22,330
Oops.

186
00:14:26,180 --> 00:14:29,250
<i>Crystal Heart... </i>

187
00:14:32,250 --> 00:14:35,760
I actually studied gravity spells,
thinking it might be on our test!

188
00:14:35,910 --> 00:14:38,760
Turns out I was prepared for this!

189
00:15:10,240 --> 00:15:12,500
The Heart...
where's the Crystal--

190
00:15:12,510 --> 00:15:15,160
Here! It rolled over to me
when you dropped it!

191
00:15:15,310 --> 00:15:16,380
Don't move!

192
00:15:18,700 --> 00:15:20,950
You can move, just not toward me!

193
00:15:25,950 --> 00:15:27,650
How could I have been so foolish...?

194
00:15:27,800 --> 00:15:29,430
I was just so eager to get it!

195
00:15:29,880 --> 00:15:31,860
Then when I saw what
was going on outside, I...

196
00:15:32,010 --> 00:15:33,690
You have to get out of there, Twilight!

197
00:15:33,840 --> 00:15:35,990
You have to be the one who brings
the Crystal Heart to Princess Cadance!

198
00:15:36,410 --> 00:15:38,990
If you don't,
you'll fail Celestia's test!

199
00:15:39,350 --> 00:15:41,870
King Sombra is already attacking
the Empire.

200
00:15:42,020 --> 00:15:44,550
He could reach the Crystal Ponies
at any moment...

201
00:15:44,700 --> 00:15:48,450
reach Princess Cadance,
my brother, my friends...

202
00:15:48,600 --> 00:15:51,700
There may not be enough time for me
to find a way to escape.

203
00:15:57,010 --> 00:16:00,390
You have to be the one
to bring the Crystal Heart to the fair.

204
00:16:00,540 --> 00:16:02,100
Me? But Twilight--

205
00:16:02,250 --> 00:16:04,260
Go.
Go!

206
00:16:12,430 --> 00:16:15,940
Don't y'all worry
your pretty little crystal heads!

207
00:16:16,090 --> 00:16:19,150
The real Crystal Heart
will be here any second!

208
00:16:19,240 --> 00:16:21,250
I don't know if they believe you...

209
00:16:21,400 --> 00:16:23,700
Don't know if I believe me...

210
00:16:31,440 --> 00:16:33,760
He's back! I can't take it!

211
00:16:36,810 --> 00:16:38,090
King Sombra...

212
00:16:38,400 --> 00:16:42,550
<i>My crystal slaves... </i>

213
00:16:47,800 --> 00:16:50,140
- Hey! Up here!
- Spike?

214
00:16:50,290 --> 00:16:51,720
I got the Crystal Heart!

215
00:16:53,540 --> 00:16:55,920
<i>That is mine! </i>

216
00:17:06,060 --> 00:17:07,770
Spikey-Wikey!

217
00:17:30,360 --> 00:17:32,890
Behold! The Crystal Princess!

218
00:17:34,060 --> 00:17:36,200
The Crystal Heart has returned.

219
00:17:36,350 --> 00:17:40,750
Use the light and love within you
to ensure that King Sombra does not.

220
00:17:52,450 --> 00:17:57,760
<i>What?
No... No! Stop! </i>

221
00:18:52,590 --> 00:18:54,300
Good job, Spike.

222
00:19:01,200 --> 00:19:03,240
I do so wish it was permanent.

223
00:19:03,390 --> 00:19:06,000
Did you see how
my mane just absolutely sparkled?

224
00:19:06,150 --> 00:19:09,750
But... good things are better
when they're a rarity.

225
00:19:10,350 --> 00:19:12,030
Everything's gonna be okay.

226
00:19:12,570 --> 00:19:16,750
You've gotta stop saving my rump like this,
it's starting to get embarrassing.

227
00:19:17,750 --> 00:19:21,380
Wasn't me who saved you in the end.
It was Spike.

228
00:19:21,530 --> 00:19:24,400
It's just a test.
Maybe she'll let you retake it.

229
00:19:24,790 --> 00:19:26,990
I don't think she's gonna
give me a new test.

230
00:19:31,910 --> 00:19:35,980
Keep it together, buddy...
gotta stay strong... for Twilight...

231
00:19:36,190 --> 00:19:37,680
It's beautiful.

232
00:19:37,830 --> 00:19:40,470
I wish it had been me
who ultimately made it so.

233
00:19:41,100 --> 00:19:42,300
But it wasn't.

234
00:19:42,450 --> 00:19:44,360
Twilight,
as I understand it,

235
00:19:44,510 --> 00:19:46,690
Spike brought Princess Cadance
the Crystal Heart

236
00:19:46,840 --> 00:19:50,650
because you weren't sure how quickly
you could find a way to escape the tower.

237
00:19:50,990 --> 00:19:55,150
You weren't willing to risk the future
of the citizens of the Crystal Empire

238
00:19:55,300 --> 00:19:58,160
in an effort to guarantee your own.

239
00:19:58,310 --> 00:20:02,200
Far better that I have a student who
understands the meaning of self-sacrifice

240
00:20:02,350 --> 00:20:05,500
than one who only looks out
for her own best interests.

241
00:20:05,650 --> 00:20:06,950
Does this mean...?

242
00:20:09,960 --> 00:20:11,900
She's totally gonna lose it!

243
00:20:13,070 --> 00:20:17,150
Keep it together, buddy...
gotta stay strong... for Twilight...!

244
00:20:19,300 --> 00:20:21,100
I passed!

245
00:20:25,790 --> 00:20:29,730
<i>You were prepared to do your best </i>

246
00:20:29,880 --> 00:20:33,370
<i>Had what it takes to pass the test </i>

247
00:20:33,520 --> 00:20:36,810
